gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a95f12c4a5bd6986d03bcc986c325e3dd3daf29","tid":109351,"uid":79539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T02:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>精神科是偽科學</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇邊個層面，如果心理學就真係得個講字，同中醫差不多，但去到腦神經，講用藥，大腦運作，都係好科學"},{"pid":"5ed5ee7ffc0ebde342cf6590a55df186e4db66ad","tid":109351,"uid":79539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T02:22:21.000Z","msg":"如果太貴，唯有去淘寶"},{"pid":"960f138747dc0204b60689573157c0d629a948d4","tid":109351,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T02:26:04.000Z","msg":"你個username咪答左自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafd119d44c1ead7a7948562bf77d2dbc4ceee9a","tid":109351,"uid":11331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T02:41:50.000Z","msg":"psyche"},{"pid":"7683b2ba1bbc1216b7cd752e69bfb9d53a7969cf","tid":109351,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T02:47:28.000Z","msg":"仲洗問精神科啦呢個病好以冇得醫食藥只係減輕病情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83dd440b265875795ee67c0b802da64b84966544","tid":109351,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T02:48:25.000Z","msg":"去睇精神科啦<br />\n普通科未必有藥"}]}